<h1>React 19.2 &lt;Activity&gt; — Client Side Rendering</h1>

<p>
  This page client-renders (<code>prerender: false</code>) the
  <code>ActivityTabSwitcher</code> component. The inactive tab stays mounted inside
  <code>&lt;Activity mode="hidden"&gt;</code>, so its input state survives tab switches
  while its effects are deactivated. Requires React 19.2+ in the app bundle.
  See <code>docs/oss/building-features/react-19-activity.md</code>.
</p>

<%= react_component("ActivityTabSwitcher",
  props: { initialTab: "profile" },
  prerender: false,
  id: "ActivityTabSwitcher-react-component-0") %>
